Package: skmle
Title: Sieve Kernel Maximum Likelihood Estimation for Survival Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dayu Sun [aut, cre] (<dayu.sun@example.com>)
Maintainer: Dayu Sun <dayu.sun@example.com>
Description: Implements the smoothed maximum likelihood estimation (skmle) method with efficient C++ backend using Rcpp, enabling fast estimation of semiparametric transformation models. Provides kernel-weighted and sieve estimators for transformed hazards models with sparse longitudinal covariates.
